channel.title: Help with TestScape and making new server please!
channel.description:
Hi, I'm new. As you can tell by my name, I'm terrible with comps :P. So anyway I was reading an insteresting post on how to make your own server and I needed a source... I've heard many sources contain viruses and stuff so I was hoping i could get a link to a TestScape download becuz I've heard it's very reliable. I also got to a point where I needed to enter my default gateway into the browser, now Im on a belkin F5D7231-4 and it asked me for a password once i reached the place, but I think the password has been customized and I was wonder if there was another way to get to it because my Parents are on holidays for 2 weeks and I don't know the password. So If there's anyway to help either of these probs help is greatly appreciated! If not, don't worry, you don't have to help me cuz I know it gets annoying helping noobs all the time.
I'll post more if I have any other probs... Hope youd don't mind lol :P
